    "text": "Classification: Parks\n\nUnion Square, at East 14th Street, and Broadway, northward, showing Union Square West (B'Way) on the left, and Union Square East (4th Ave.) on the right. Buildings observed across Union Square Park, are on the north side of East 17th Street. The Metropolitan tower appears across the skyline.\n\nOctober 1924.\n\nGeneral Electric Company.\n",
